definitions.definition: The god of wine , ivy and grapes , specifically its intoxication and social influence, but also the patron of agriculture and the theater . Also related to the mystery of religion, as in "spiritual intoxication".

main_definition: ( Greek mythology ) The god of wine , ivy and grapes , specifically its intoxication and social influence, but also the patron of agriculture and the theater . Also related to the mystery of religion, as in "spiritual intoxication".
